{"tid":1787441,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有無卡通片係有大量警暴影像？","createTime":"2019-12-18T02:25:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-18T04:55:32.000Z","uid":89966,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"531de2acb5a5d5ecaa67961e50c2aef3dc2ca891","tid":1787441,"uid":89966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T02:25:25.000Z","msg":"要永續呢場運動<br />\n就要將警察=暴力觀念灌輸比下一代<br />\n就好似早幾年外國youtube好多cp.血腥.等等元素滲透落兒童卡通片咁<br />\n我地要日繼日年繼年教育幼稚園bb小學生<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n例如一套卡通片開頭正正常常<br />\n到中段突然有班綠曱出現<br />\n大量開槍煙霧離漫流血場面<br />\n再有black bloc手足上前線反抗<br />\n最後比綠曱打到爆晒缸⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n總之乜撚嘢卡通人物最後都比防暴殺死<br />\n唔洗講咩tg二噁英一國兩制五大訴求咁複雜<br />\n呢啲簡單直接嘅畫面最易渲染到小朋友<br />\n藍絲父母愈禁細路就愈想睇<br />\n要小朋友一開youtube就見到呢類片有無得諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1f26b3e0e3b7b3ea22663a34b9752bd240d1964","tid":1787441,"uid":89966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T02:27:20.000Z","msg":"要狗仔狗女為自己父母感到羞恥<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8d295624d526166ed975e96251e14a6e45747d5","tid":1787441,"uid":89966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T02:28:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"984472308e0f5531935b4c8c385dcdc766a33fd4","tid":1787441,"uid":89966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T02:29:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a0ad028509fde5c7ad3c208015fd0e8f6af959c9","tid":1787441,"uid":286206,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T02:31:01.000Z","msg":"銀英傳係球場衝入去搞和平示威果段<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最終變真暴動<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd43bfbe4bac6b0bbe7a37d028bd534f5c31b655","tid":1787441,"uid":89966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a0ad028509fde5c7ad3c208015fd0e8f6af959c9","tid":1787441,"uid":286206,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T02:31:01.000Z","msg":"銀英傳係球場衝入去搞和平示威果段<img